                    "message": {
                        "text": "Reentrancy in PharmaCompany.buyMedicine(string,address,uint256,address,uint256) (../sb/SupplyChain_F.sol#4060-4066):\n\tExternal calls:\n\t- require(bool,string)(IHospitalManagement(hospital).authorizeSale(prescriptionId,to,medicineName,amount),Sale not authorized) (../sb/SupplyChain_F.sol#4064)\n\t- _safeTransferFrom(owner(),to,medicines[medicineName],amount,bytes(medicineName)) (../sb/SupplyChain_F.sol#4065)\n\t\t- response = IERC1155Receiver(to).onERC1155Received(operator,from,id,value,data) (../sb/SupplyChain_F.sol#574-588)\n\t\t- response = IERC1155Receiver(to).onERC1155BatchReceived(operator,from,ids,values,data) (../sb/SupplyChain_F.sol#609-625)\n\t\t- ERC1155Utils.checkOnERC1155Received(operator,from,to,id,value,data) (../sb/SupplyChain_F.sol#3712)\n\t\t- ERC1155Utils.checkOnERC1155BatchReceived(operator,from,to,ids,values,data) (../sb/SupplyChain_F.sol#3714)\n\tState variables written after the call(s):\n\t- _safeTransferFrom(owner(),to,medicines[medicineName],amount,bytes(medicineName)) (../sb/SupplyChain_F.sol#4065)\n\t\t- _balances[id][from] = fromBalance - value (../sb/SupplyChain_F.sol#3672)\n\t\t- _balances[id][to] += value (../sb/SupplyChain_F.sol#3677)\n\tERC1155._balances (../sb/SupplyChain_F.sol#3541) can be used in cross function reentrancies:\n\t- ERC1155._update(address,address,uint256[],uint256[]) (../sb/SupplyChain_F.sol#3654-3688)\n\t- ERC1155.balanceOf(address,uint256) (../sb/SupplyChain_F.sol#3578-3580)\n"
